  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/tabletpcs/\" rel=\"tag\">平板电脑</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2013/10/19/dont-bother-trying-to-upgrade-to-windows-rt-8-1-today/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/windowsrt81lead01.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在阅读本文之时，恰巧地想到你要将你的 Windows RT 装置升上 Windows RT 8.1 的话，可以先不动手了。Microsoft 刚刚宣布发现一项「影响少数用户的事故」，因而暂时将 Windows RT 8.1 的升级从 Windows Store 上下架。可是，他们并没有真正地解释这项事故是什麽，但有消息指出似乎问题是有关用户在升级後不能正常启动装置。Microsoft 目前正在抢救，所以大家要多加留意我们後续的报导了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/19/dont-bother-trying-to-upgrade-to-windows-rt-8-1-today/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2013/10/19/microsoft-yanks-windows-rt-8-1-update-temporarily-following-discovery-of-a-situation/?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+Techcrunch+%28TechCrunch%29\">TechCrunch</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/19/dont-bother-trying-to-upgrade-to-windows-rt-8-1-today/\">Microsoft</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/19/dont-bother-trying-to-upgrade-to-windows-rt-8-1-today/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20749682/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/19/dont-bother-trying-to-upgrade-to-windows-rt-8-1-today/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
